{"tid":1890625,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［RIP]曹捷先生（陶傑）撰文悼念亡父：若他魂行未遠，願他庇佑香港，因為我是他兒子，也是香港人的兒子","createTime":"2020-02-21T09:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T22:54:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d9430417d21860535cf4659be7696bc9433f9d54","tid":1890625,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26XrCXv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26XrCXv.png&h=8f060e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n父親曹驥雲與我1962年底在青山容龍別墅。我記得身上穿的那件毛衣，不記得那一天。<br />\n<br />\n他原籍桂林，南京出生，他出生後母親亡故，有一姊一兄，相繼於逃難時病歿。一九五〇年，他手持一隻皮箱由南京上海輾轉渡過羅湖橋來香港，投奔他的姨媽王李象珮女士。而他的姨丈是當年香港紗廠寧波老闆王啟宇，亦即王統元、王福元兄弟之父。<br />\n<br />\n他在香港看的第一部英語電影，叫做「郎心如鐵」（A Place in the Sun）。他很喜歡這部電影。後來我長大了一看，見到片中的男主角孟甘穆利奇里夫，飾演一個鄉下青年，到大城市投靠一個富豪親戚。然後發生許多事情。那一刻，我才發現我多認識了父親。<br />\n<br />\n華人社會的父子關係很複雜，而這個世界本來就不大。他有一點值得一記的故事，而他進入了香港的報界。<br />\n<br />\n他是一個平凡人，但經歷的時代苦難，見識過巨大變遷。我從小跟隨他，所見所聞，由側面見識了一個宏大的舊新交替中國，也體驗了香港的成長。<br />\n<br />\n今天凌晨兩點半，我在他的病榻前，說：「我和你此生緣淡，唯言罕情怯，若有來生，如你不棄，我願意再做你的兒子。」<br />\n<br />\n他聽到了，眼角垂下淚珠。<br />\n<br />\n感謝許多朋友的慰勉。在這個艱困的時刻，我想起童年的香港，成千上萬匯聚在維多利亞港的皮箱和腳印。父親離逝於此時，上天若有啟迪，若他魂行未遠，願他庇佑苦難中的香港，因為我不但是他兒子，也是香港人的兒子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/tokit.channel/?__tn__=%2Cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252Cg&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVFFFw%2Fpr%2F0Xu32W9HouEUHQ%3D&h=bcc54a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/tokit.channel/?__tn__=%2Cg</a>"},{"pid":"d1e5bd5a37e44ee5afab8c57d57a5cf9758baf3a","tid":1890625,"uid":38535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"ae2801bef45f6868a64f4cd80fbabf19f4b247fe","tid":1890625,"uid":240608,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"9十幾歲，算係咁啦<br />\n<br />\n個仔係香江四大才子 幾威"},{"pid":"a3fa9a62d17db6d3cd233bb0a5286076cb901d9e","tid":1890625,"uid":61547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:51:40.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感覺上佢放棄 係度等死"},{"pid":"62c80e94cd1e4548a42d5620d8fb96d1a83d2eef","tid":1890625,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"0dc2a140393e39e882841c1287e28d174cbe9eca","tid":1890625,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:52:59.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"25b0b6e0c6f1329474593fff7b065a1e3eaf958b","tid":1890625,"uid":177510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9861aab084f2ae9e19e17a43b7cc148c10419718","tid":1890625,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"［悼念721］今晚7-8點 元朗、銅鑼灣、馬鞍山、杏花邨、香港仔 有人發起靜坐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da4ecfb16f0fd6cbe97b4bf51f90abfa2da56609","tid":1890625,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP 陶生振作"},{"pid":"a61b16fbe73be6714ae38e31151330c474d6b6ed","tid":1890625,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"佢老豆個人生好富傳奇色彩"},{"pid":"e00902491cbb85ee28276c69e02484d9a87c8d92","tid":1890625,"uid":175499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"RIP<br />\n九十幾歲都算有福了，希望佢係上面過得開心"},{"pid":"2785780459d593a323e0e0955983c83b8bc850ae","tid":1890625,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"19老豆 好似系請個馬姐湊大 19<img src=\"/assets/fac